data.description: Welcome to your future home in the desirable Murphy Creek community, conveniently located for access to Downtown Denver, DIA, Buckley SFB, and Denver Tech Center. This recently updated 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home features an open and functional layout with an abundance of light. A soaring vaulted ceiling adds to the spaciousness of the front living room, which flows into a second living room and fully updated kitchen with new Samsung stainless-steel appliances (8/2023) and granite countertops (8/2023). A gas-burning fireplace is perfect for cozy nights, adding ambience and warmth. French doors open onto a spacious patio and versatile landscaped backyard--perfect for barbecuing, gardening, or even a hot tub! The residence has been refreshed with interior and exterior paint (8/2023) and new flooring throughout (8/2022). The main level features stylish, durable luxury vinyl plank that is so easy to maintain. Head upstairs to the primary bedroom, complete with en-suite bathroom and custom oversized tub. Two additional spacious bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a conveniently located laundry complete the second level. This golf course community has endless amenities just outside your front door! Enjoy the community pool, clubhouse, tennis courts, parks, and numerous trails. Or tee it up at the championship 18-hole Murphy Creek Golf Course, located just down the street. Enjoy the low maintenance yard with front and rear sprinkler system, while keeping your furry friends safe in the fully fenced back-yard. Pre-K thru 8th grade school is just a 5 minute walk from the home, the high-school a mere 5 minute drive. Easy access to E-470, DIA, Buckley Space Force Base, Southlands Mall, and a multitude of shopping and dining options. Schedule your showing today!
